ue">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/now-fighting-inside-gaza-tunnels-idf-knows-that-killing-hamas-leaders-wont-end-its-rule/0000018d-572b-d0fc-a9bd-5f7fa3850000</guid></item><item><title>总理办公室同意修复内塔尼亚胡私人住宅泳池后，以色列官员辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-official-to-quit-after-pms-bureau-okays-repairs-to-pool-at-netanyahus-home/0000018d-570b-d997-adff-df7becd90000</link><description>首席会计师与总理办公室其他官员发生冲突，最近一次是因为内塔尼亚胡位于凯撒利亚的庞大住宅的游泳池和住宅区的维修问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 00:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-official-to-quit-after-pms-bureau-okays-repairs-to-pool-at-netanyahus-home/0000018d-570b-d997-adff-df7becd90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战时内阁讨论哈马斯人质交易；消息人士称，大多数问题都已达成共识</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-war-cabinet-discusses-hostage-deal-sources-uderstandings-emerge-on-most-issues/0000018d-56be-d0fc-a9bd-5eff2c950000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡办公室否认谈判取得进展的报道，但接受国土报采访的消息人士表示，核心问题是停火问题。周一早些时候，作为谈判的一部分，以色列代表团访问了埃及</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 21:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-war-cabinet-discusses-hostage-deal-sources-uderstandings-emerge-on-most-issues/0000018d-56be-d0fc-a9bd-5eff2c950000</guid></item><item><title>“你在他们的鲜血上跳舞”：以色列人质家庭对重新安置会议感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/youre-dancing-on-their-blood-hostage-families-outraged-over-resettlement-conference/0000018d-5679-d0fc-a9bd-5e7d6c8b0000</link><description>以色列人质家属在议会发言，指责出席会议的内塔尼亚胡政府十一位部长“放弃他们”，而人质协议仍未达成</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 19:52:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/youre-dancing-on-their-blood-hostage-families-outraged-over-resettlement-conference/0000018d-5679-d0fc-a9bd-5e7d6c8b0000</guid></item><item><title>美国称以色列加沙重新安置的呼吁“鲁莽”，本格维尔加倍努力驱逐“试点”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/u-s-says-calls-for-gaza-settlement-reckless-as-ben-gvir-doubles-down-on-expulsion-pilot/0000018d-560a-d0fc-a9bd-5e5f15200000</link><description>在呼吁犹太人重新安置加沙的会议一天后，本-格维尔强调，在中间派战时内阁部长批评这次会议后，巴勒斯坦人的自愿移民至关重要。美国、法国和德国也谴责这些呼吁“不负责任”</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 19:32:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/u-s-says-calls-for-gaza-settlement-reckless-as-ben-gvir-doubles-down-on-expulsion-pilot/0000018d-560a-d0fc-a9bd-5e5f15200000</guid></item><item><title>以色列情报报告指责近东救济工程处 190 名工作人员是“顽固”武装分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/israel-accuses-190-unrwa-staff-of-being-hardened-militants-intel-memo-alleges/0000018d-5637-d0fc-a9bd-5e7fcbd50000</link><description>以色列公布的一份长达六页的档案称，近东救济工程处 13,000 名员工中，有 10% 与哈马斯有一般联系，其中有 190 名“杀手” ■ 10 个国家已停止向该机构提供资金</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 18:23:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/israel-accuses-190-unrwa-staff-of-being-hardened-militants-intel-memo-alleges/0000018d-5637-d0fc-a9bd-5e7fcbd50000</guid></item><item><title>具有新纳粹根源的瑞典极右政党高层成员在以色列议会会见以色列部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/top-members-of-far-right-swedish-party-with-neo-nazi-roots-meet-israeli-minister/0000018d-564e-d0fc-a9bd-5e5f9ff00000</link><description>由于瑞典民主党成员表达了反犹太主义和仇视伊斯兰教的情绪，以色列迄今为止一直没有与瑞典民主党接触。党员告诉《国土报》，他们在访问期间会见了几位部长，但拒绝透露他们的姓名</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 18:08:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/top-members-of-far-right-swedish-party-with-neo-nazi-roots-meet-israeli-minister/0000018d-564e-d0fc-a9bd-5e5f9ff00000</guid></item><item><title>以上帝之名进行种族清洗：唯一对加沙“后天”有计划的以色列人</title><link>https: