929d20000</link><description>总理表示，提出这一要求的原因是他的律师的家人生病了。在另外两起刑事案件中代表内塔尼亚胡的律师阿米特·哈达德表示，他也愿意在贿赂案中代表他</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 15:52:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-defense-attorney-in-bribery-case-asks-to-step-down/0000018d-54e1-d1b6-aded-5fe929d20000</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，近东救济工程处在加沙的大约 10% 员工与哈马斯、伊斯兰圣战组织有联系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/wsj-about-10-percent-of-unrwa-employees-in-gaza-have-ties-to-hamas-islamic-jihad/0000018d-5565-d8cc-a1fd-576f89eb0000</link><description>以色列官员向《华尔街日报》报道称，参与加沙哈马斯活动的联合国巴勒斯坦难民机构（近东救济工程处）雇员数量“不仅仅是几个害群之马”。随着指控的继续调查，九个国家已暂时停止向该组织提供资金</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 15:36:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/wsj-about-10-percent-of-unrwa-employees-in-gaza-have-ties-to-hamas-islamic-jihad/0000018d-5565-d8cc-a1fd-576f89eb0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列人民将解决加沙问题”：内塔尼亚胡的部长们在极右翼会议上支持驱逐巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-people-of-israel-will-settle-gaza-netanyahu-ministers-urge-palestinians-expulsion/0000018d-5495-d1b6-aded-5fdd570c0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的通讯部长在台上宣称，“自愿”[移民]有时是你强加的情况，直到他们同意为止。”他揭露了“以色列胜利会议”的真实信息：转移或驱逐，来自加沙的巴勒斯坦人</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 15:32:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-people-of-israel-will-settle-gaza-netanyahu-ministers-urge-palestinians-expulsion/0000018d-5495-d1b6-aded-5fdd570c0000</guid></item><item><title>不仅是加沙：自战争以来，西岸巴勒斯坦人买不起食物和药品</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/not-only-gaza-west-bank-palestinians-cannot-afford-food-and-meds-since-the-war/0000018d-556e-d0fc-a9bd-5f7f03930000</link><description>加沙战争对约旦河西岸的经济造成严重破坏：商店关门，企业停止接受非现金付款，巴勒斯坦工人不吃饭，孩子们几乎没有足够的食物</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 14:28:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/not-only-gaza-west-bank-palestinians-cannot-afford-food-and-meds-since-the-war/0000018d-556e-d0fc-a9bd-5f7f03930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在海法发生撞击后受重伤；袭击者用斧头射击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-seriously-wounded-after-ramming-in-haifa-assailant-with-axe-shot/0000018d-5489-dfdc-a5ad-deff8ba60000</link><description>这名士兵在海军基地附近被一名袭击者碾压受伤，袭击者随后携带斧头下车，被一名以色列国防军军官开枪射击。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 12:27:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-seriously-wounded-after-ramming-in-haifa-assailant-with-axe-shot/0000018d-5489-dfdc-a5ad-deff8ba60000</guid></item><item><title>想离开加沙吗？支付我们 10,000 美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/want-out-of-gaza-pay-us-10-000/0000018d-54ee-df5c-a1ad-54ff690e0000</link><description>在加沙，在流离失所的加沙人试图躲避以色列的炸弹的影响下，进入埃及的拉法口岸的贿赂业正在蓬勃发展。埃及否认这一点，但一名埃及研究人员表示，“开罗最高官员”参与其中</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 11:46:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/want-out-of-gaza-pay-us-10-000/0000018d-54ee-df5c-a1ad-54ff690e0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦诉拜登：“我的家人被我的钱杀害了。”新闻。拜登可以结束这一切”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/my-family-is-being-killed-on-my-dime-pres-biden-could-put-an-end-to-this/0000018d-54b3-df5c-a1ad-54f7a03e0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 10:28:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/my-family-is-being-killed-on-my-dime-pres-biden-could-put-an-end-to-this/0000018d-54b3-df5c-a1ad-54f7a03e0000</guid></item>